{"tid":2236453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1,500 黃店響應「全民感謝日」　籲支持民間小店　望續關注 12 港人","createTime":"2020-10-09T12:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T13:05:22.000Z","uid":271829,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8806023d5601f2c9d740f7fd40edaf8db970968d","tid":2236453,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/120818039_109980927542854_3082833739434392951_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=CWl_f0k7RUUAX_wLwo5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=84c683a54bc870ef83793933be83550d&amp;oe=5FA57ABF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F120818039_109980927542854_3082833739434392951_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DCWl_f0k7RUUAX_wLwo5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D84c683a54bc870ef83793933be83550d%26oe%3D5FA57ABF&h=520c99a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n反送中運動衍生出「黃店」概念，不少支持運動的市民都提倡多去「黃店」，抵制「藍店」，組成「黃色經濟圈」。運動爆發至今已超過 1 年，有商戶在網上呼籲本周末（10、11 日）發起「全民感謝日」，組織黃店推出促銷活動，至今全港已經有超過 1,500 間黃店響應。感謝日團隊亦已經印製了 10 萬張文宣卡，呼籲市民繼續留意「12 港人事件」。<br />\n「10.10 全民感謝日」Facebook 專頁提供了參與感謝日的參加表格，並且不斷更新參與感謝日的黃店名單，遍布港九新界。專頁又說，商戶除了努力促銷，市民努力消費外，亦呼籲各位繼續關心「12 港人」。<br />\n...<br />\n10.10全民感謝日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/10.10.thankfulweek/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F10.10.thankfulweek%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=919541b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/10.10.thankfulweek/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/1-500-黃店響應-全民感謝日-籲支持民間小店-望續關注-12-港人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F1-500-%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89-%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E6%97%A5-%E7%B1%B2%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97-%E6%9C%9B%E7%B